snippet.title: Trailer - GRAN TURISMO TV E3 2008 Trailer for PS3
snippet.description: CGR Trailers presents a GRAN TURISMO TV 2008 E3 trailer. This trailer features Gran Turismo TV which is a distribution system setup through the PlayStaiton Network (PSN) and is with Gran Turismo 5 Prologue on the PlayStation 3 (PS3).
